cmmbqdskl01fnb2it8c816i45	Oof Fighters	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	{}	Join us for the ooF Fighters, Lonestar Supernova, and Wicked Vixxen on Saturday, March 27th! Get ready for a full-throttle tribute to rock legends Foo Fighters. Austin&rsquo;s Oof Fighters recreate the electrifying live energy, massive sound, and unforgettable anthems that have defined generations of fans. Formed by veteran musicians from across the country, The Oof Fighters deliver a powerful, authentic concert experience packed with hits, fan favorites, and nonstop crowd energy. If you&rsquo;ve ever wanted to feel the rush of a Foo Fighters show... this is your chance. Loud guitars. Huge choruses. Zero chill. | Lonestar Supernova, Wicked Vixxen	\N	\N	2026-03-04 07:44:23.013	2026-03-04 07:44:23.013	\N	\N	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N
