cmm0cw5ap000ug7ittl7xquks	cmlvapuw1003dmyitvh8c5ave	3663901385314260424	🔥 **WORM SUICIDE IGNITED KICK BUTT COFFEE!** 🔥 \nLast night, Austin’s punk heartbeat pounded at the legendary Kick Butt Coffee as the mighty **Worm Suicide** unleashed pure sonic fury! Celebrating over **28 relentless years** of skum-rock-infused hardcore, these South Texas originals (now Austin mainstays) proved why they’re revered. (28 years old..1st show Thanksgiving\n1997. Band created in 1996. Their raw, old-school punk energy was a masterclass in unrelenting power.\n\n**Pablo Flores** commanded the chaos with primal, snarling lead vocals that cut through the sweat-drenched air. The dual guitar attack was ferocious: **Scott Free** shredded blistering leads and roared backup vocals, while **Thomas Grant** locked in the relentless rhythm guitar and added crucial vocal grit. The foundation was rock-solid thanks to **Zach Findley**’s driving, thunderous bass lines and fierce backup shouts, while **Jett Baker** pummeled the kit with unstoppable, precision aggression. Together, they were tighter than barbed wire and twice as dangerous.\n\nKick Butt Coffee provided the perfect, intimate crucible for this chaos – its legendary vibe and awesome staff fostering an electrifying communion between band and die-hard fans. This was punk history alive: a blistering set from a band that’s shared stages with legends and conquered compilations (Samhain, Misfits, GG Allin!). Their legendary endurance and 2020 vinyl triumph resonate louder than ever. Pure. Adrenaline. Punk. Perfection.\n\n#WormSuicide #KickButtCoffee #AustinLiveMusic #TexasPunk #OldSchoolPunk #SkumRock #PunkRock #LiveMusicAustin #SupportLocalMusic #PunkLives #23YearsStrong	2025-06-27 02:26:20	https://www.instagram.com/p/DLYyuXTt9XI/	2026-02-24 08:41:16.753	https://scontent-hou1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/511485782_2144320596072632_1727531754428338016_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-hou1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ