cmm0d5zc7002cg7itlzec6168	cmlvav5k000aymyit470o4y6o	3732566652631479863	🚨ARTIST ANNOUNCEMENT🚨\n\nLONESTAR MASSACRE\n\nACT III\n\nLoud and Local Fest\n\nWe are STOKED to announce that @lonestarmassacretx will be performing at this year’s Loud and Local Fest! What ELSE is happening at the show? Well……\n\nThis show is a fundraiser event for The Rock Box/Vibes Event Center/Vibes Underground and consists of three parts, or ACTs. (Yes, the 5 dollar entry donation covers all three!) Let us explain.\n\nAct I is from 12:00 - 1:00 PM and will just be an hour of request only music in The Rock Room, while our Vendors are Rocking and Rolling in the Vibes Event Center room ready to meet you and show off their goodies! 👀👀 Patrons will have access to Vendors throughout the ENTIRE event :)\n\nACT II is when the music starts! This portion of the show will take place between 1 pm and 4:35 pm and will feature music from some of San Antonio’s Local Indie, Cumbia, and Emo Artists:\n\n@emo.her0 \n@tarasco_tropical \n@therockmorton\n\nACT III. This is when we pick it up a notch! ACT III will take place from 6-10PM and will consist of 4 Metal Artists!\n\n@lonestarmassacretx \n@snake_fathertx \n@immortalexecution \n@trenchbornband \n\nFAQ’s\n\nWill we have to re enter for each Act? No! Naming the different sections of the show as “ACTs” is just a fun way for us to organize the chaos. By all means, come to the show and stay all day! We will have plenty of activities, music, vendors, and drinks!\n\nI heard there will be raffles. Will there be raffles? Yes! We are having 3 raffles at this event and they will be announced later this week!\n\nIs this an all ages event? Indeed! Feel free to bring the fam! \n\nThere is a lot more coming so stay tuned for more information on the first Loud and Local Fest and The Rock Box in San Antonio TX!\n\n🤘🏼🤘🏼🖤🖤💪🏼💪🏼🖤🖤🤘🏼🤘🏼🖤🖤💪🏼💪🏼\n🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵🎵\n\nWHILE YOU WAIT….\nTake some time and check out the other photos of past events in ALL THREE of our rooms! See you all soon!	2025-09-29 20:10:40	https://www.instagram.com/p/DPMvZg2kXY3/	2026-02-24 08:48:55.591	https://scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/554989393_18046900313669720_1566703357377115683_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2QEJLpbt86xRoOl4FqqaJ5-WxZ97bBGG14n-V7Bf5vi43QuV3USMr8oZn72PR4luu24&_nc_ohc=nWyDe5bsxosQ7kNvwFcjUEp&_nc_gid=H7-YTPjOimRnbOh5m70gug&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AfsZRGBNH5qOiCv8x1rgEcnPiA--CURBbEZIcWgEtLbxwA&oe=69A34D3C&_nc_sid=10d13b
