cmmbpjyj500j7b2itkegwxnh4	cmmbpjyib00ixb2itm21qtnbq	\N	Over two weeks later and I’m still processing my first Big Blues Bender. 💜 At that sold-out HART Fund show, I shared Rain—a song I wrote to honor the children airlifted out of Vietnam, like me, during Operation Babylift, 50 years after the Fall of Saigon.\n\nVets who were there hugged me after, apologizing, asking what happened to us. Moments I’ll never forget. Special thanks to Nick Schnebelen, Mike Merritt, David Kida, and Red Young for playing your ❤️s out. 🥹\n\nThis clip is just a piece of that night. Watch the full story & performance here:\n👉 https://youtu.be/DdtjEw5ITdE\n\n#BigBluesBender #HARTFund #OperationBabylift #FallOfSaigon50 #Vietnam #BluesMusic #Rain	2025-10-03 07:10:07	\N	2026-03-04 07:21:11.057	\N
