cmmbpsm1z00nwb2it9epg1mnx	cmmbpsm1100nsb2itecdtruqt	\N	My first single Waitress is out !!! \n\nI couldn’t be more excited and proud. 🥹 I don’t even know what happened, i just started making music on garageband w my scarlett interface and somehow created this gem of a song. I think you’ll like it :) give it a listen, give it a share, especially if you’ve ever worked in the service industry 🫡🫡🫡☕️☕️☕️ sometimes we have bigger and better dreams than refilling coffee mugs, running mediocre food, having to explain something on the menu you know nothing about, dropping a plate and shattering it on the next table of guests, or spilling an entire bottle of wine on a table (yes that did happen to me when I worked at the spotted pig lol) but we do it all w grace because we know it’s just the stepping stone in our journey of life and our dreams will come true 🫶\n\nNo more tables , from now on I’m only serving c^nt \n\n💔☕️🍽️💔☕️🍽️💔☕️🍽️💔 \n❣️❣️❣️❣️❣️❣️❣️❣️❣️❣️\nLink 🔗 in bio to save and listen ✨\n\nWritten, composed/ produced by me \n\nCo-produced, mixed and mastered by the insanely talented  @jcbarrettmusic (literally made it sound sooooo good and magical) ily !\n\nPhotos by @camilleadrianephotography ilysm !!! 🥰🥹 literally a dream these photos	2026-01-17 00:20:28	\N	2026-03-04 07:27:54.791	\N
